QuestData.Title: Meet With Avaros Dawnglaive
QuestData.Description: Avaros Dawnglaive sent an urgent message for you, $n. He asks you to join him at The Barracks in Orgrimmar's Valley of Honor the next time you're in the city. It sounds as though he must have an important assignment for you.
QuestData.LogDescription: Speak with Avaros Dawnglaive at The Barracks in Orgrimmar.
QuestData.QuestCompletionLog: Speak with Avaros Dawnglaive at The Barracks in Orgrimmar.
